I entered "The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog" into Google translate, and the result was "দ্রুত গাঢ় শেয়াল অলস কুকুর জুড়ে জাম্প". Then I created a PDF file with this. With your font, I got a line with incomplete glyphs:
[example-new.pdf](https://github.com/apache/pdfbox/files/1910334/example-new.pdf)
Code:
```
                PDFont font7 = PDType0Font.load(document, new File("Lohit-Bengali.ttf"));
                stream.setFont(font7, 12);
                stream.newLine();
                stream.showText("দ্রুত গাঢ় শেয়াল অলস কুকুর জুড়ে জাম্প");
```
